ns. If you agree, BNYM team are happy to directly get in touch with your co=
ntacts at HSBC. Please let us know the relevant contacts. Once the wire is =
returned, BNYM team will then update and resend.

Thank you for your patience on this matter.

Kind regards,
Mehmet

