<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Hi Adam,<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We wanted=
 to follow-up on the below regarding the PBN wire. We spoke with Bank of Ne=
w York Mellon and they will add the BIC and Account number in reference to =
field 70 as provided by HSBC. BNYM team
 would like to confirm with HSBC all required fields moving forward to prev=
ent any further complications. If you agree, BNYM team are happy to directl=
y get in touch with your contacts at HSBC. Please let us know the relevant =
contacts. Once the wire is returned,
 BNYM team will then update and resend. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 for your patience on this matter.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Kind rega=
rds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
