<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Hi Adam<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Have passed the below to BNYM and asked them to reso=
lve first thing on Monday.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Apologies for all the back and forth on this!<o:p></=
o:p></p>
