<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">The wire was processed last week on 26 May so you should have rece=
ived the cash.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
