<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">No, the transfer did not succeed. Here's what the ba=
nk says about the SWIFT instruction you sent to me:<o:p></o:p></p>
